Installation Instructions for 'BistaticHub' and Utilities
=========================================================

If you already have a "configure" script in this directory, build like this:

$ ./configure
$ make

Otherwise, you will need to generate a new "configure" script before following
the directions above:

$ autoscan 
[
    now edit configure.scan to create configure.in:
	Add AM_INIT_AUTOMAKE(BistaticHub, 2.0.0) after the AC_INIT line
	Add AC_PROG_CC under "dnl Checks for programs."
	Add AC_PROG_CXX under "dnl Checks for programs."
	Add AC_CHECK_LIB(netcdf, nc_open) under "dnl Checks for libraries."
	Change AC_OUTPUT() to AC_OUTPUT(Makefile)
]
$ aclocal
$ autoconf (ignore the AC_TRY_RUN warning)
$ automake --add-missing --foreign





